# Study MBBS Abroad Landing Page

This is a responsive landing page for "Study MBBS Abroad" built as part of a Front-End Development Intern application for University Insights. The page showcases top MBBS study destinations, key benefits of studying abroad, and includes a lead generation form with validation.

## Table of Contents

- [Demo](#demo)
