- [License](#license)

## Demo

A live demo of the landing page can be viewed [here](#)  
*(Replace the link with your live demo URL on Netlify/Vercel.)*

## Features

- **Hero Section:**  
  - Dynamic background image with engaging headlines and a call-to-action (CTA) button.
- **Why Study MBBS Abroad Section:**  
  - Lists key benefits such as affordable tuition, global recognition, and modern infrastructure.
- **Top Countries Section:**  
  - Evenly distributed cards for popular MBBS study destinations.
- **Lead Generation Form:**  
  - A form that collects user details with real-time JavaScript validation.
- **Responsive Design:**  
  - Fully responsive layout built using Tailwind CSS.
- **SEO & Performance:**  
  - Optimized with meta tags and tracking code for Google Analytics and Facebook Pixel.

## Technologies Used

- **HTML5**
- **Tailwind CSS**
- **JavaScript**
- **Git & GitHub**
- **Netlify/Vercel** (for deployment)

## Project Structure

study-mbbs-abroad-landing-page/
├── index.html            # Main HTML file
├── script.js             # JavaScript file for form validation and interactivity
├── styles.css            # Optional custom CSS file (if using local Tailwind setup)
├── assets/
│   └── images/
│       └── hero-bg.jpg   # Hero section background image
├── README.md             # Project documentation file


## Installation & Setup

git clone https://github.com/your-username/study-mbbs-abroad-landing-page.git
cd study-mbbs-abroad-landing-page

## Setup Tailwind CSS:
You can use the CDN for quick setup by including the following script in your <head> of index.html:
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>

## Open the Project:

Open index.html in your web browser to see the landing page.


## Deployment on Netlify:
Push your code to GitHub.
Connect your repository to Netlify and deploy.


## Usage
### Hero Section:
Displays a captivating background image with a bold headline, supportive subheading, and a strong CTA that directs users to the lead generation form.

### Country Cards:
The "Top Countries" section uses a responsive grid layout to evenly distribute country cards, each displaying a flag and country name.

### Lead Generation Form:
The form includes fields for Name, Email, Phone, and Country Preference. JavaScript is used for validating the form inputs before submission.

### Interactivity & Responsiveness:
Tailwind CSS ensures that the page is responsive across different devices, while JavaScript enhances interactivity.


